<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚7點開始就是煙火大會啦！<delay frames="40" />
光是想像那聲響和氣味，<delay20 />
就不禁讓人心跳加速咧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚就是煙火大會了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火會在晚上7點開始發射，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我得想辦法避免自己忘掉才行！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00">我好期待<delay20 />今晚7點開始的煙火大會啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你當然也會來看對吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我們一起度過一個美好的夜晚吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00">一想到煙火大會即將開始，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就緊張起來了，這真不像我啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只是看煙火而已，我緊張什麼啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也是來看煙火的吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我一想到大會即將開始，<delay20 />就冷靜不下來啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />乾脆去附近晃晃，散散心好了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我因為不想錯過第一發煙火，<delay20 />所以一直
抬頭盯著天空，結果弄得我肩膀痠痛。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明明好戲才正要開始啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我非常享受<delay8 />煙火大會喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我受到其他傢伙高漲的情緒影響，<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />忍不住大玩特玩了一番啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊——<delay20 />玩得真是盡興啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看著煙火，我的情緒也跟著高漲起來啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來今晚是睡不著了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火大會<delay8 />讓島上的氣氛變得好熱絡啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧如此，<delay8 />我也充分享受到了祭典氛圍，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這下明天就能繼續努力了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年最後的煙火大會<delay20 />已經結束啦<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然想到這是最後一場就覺得有點可惜，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但也讓我更加期待明年的大會了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年的煙火<delay8 />每個都好漂亮啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我只要一閉上雙眼，<delay8 />
就能想起當時的景色喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年的煙火大會已經結束了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我明年還想像這樣<delay frames="40" />
和你一起<delay20 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />觀賞煙火啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
</msbt>